There are notes left by other adventurers.
Perhaps someone has left a clue for you to follow...
or it could be a trap!

Maybe it is just the ramblings of an old man reliving 
memories of adventures past.

Who knows really?

Do you want to leave your own message?
Hint: $ nano message_from_your_name_here

How do you leave the box and get back to the cave?
Hint: $ cd ..
